genresAdvancedInfo.name: tunisian alternative
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Tunisian alternative music is a blend of traditional Tunisian music and modern rock and pop sounds. It often features Arabic lyrics and incorporates instruments such as the oud and darbuka. Tunisian alternative artists often use their music to explore social and political issues in their country, and the genre has become a platform for young Tunisians to express their views and connect with a wider audience. The music is energetic and often incorporates dance rhythms.
